{
  "script_id": "complex",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "欢迎来到复数实验！今天我们要探索一个神奇的数学世界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "你可能听说过，负数不能开平方。但数学家说：为什么不能？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "于是他们发明了虚数单位i，定义i的平方等于负1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "imaginary-unit",
      "line_id": "imaginary-unit-1",
      "filename": "imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "虚数单位i满足i的平方等于负1，这是它的定义。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "imaginary-unit",
      "line_id": "imaginary-unit-2",
      "filename": "imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.41,
      "size": 22608,
      "text": "有了i，我们就可以表示负数的平方根了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "imaginary-unit",
      "line_id": "imaginary-unit-3",
      "filename": "imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.99,
      "size": 47808,
      "text": "例如，负4的平方根就是2i，因为2i的平方等于4乘以i的平方，等于负4。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "imaginary-unit",
      "line_id": "imaginary-unit-4",
      "filename": "imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/imaginary-unit-imaginary-unit-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "虚数虽然叫虚，但它在物理和工程中有非常实际的应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-number",
      "line_id": "complex-number-1",
      "filename": "complex-number-complex-number-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-number-complex-number-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "复数是实数和虚数的组合，写成a加bi的形式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-number",
      "line_id": "complex-number-2",
      "filename": "complex-number-complex-number-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-number-complex-number-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "其中a叫做实部，b叫做虚部，它们都是实数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-number",
      "line_id": "complex-number-3",
      "filename": "complex-number-complex-number-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-number-complex-number-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "当b等于0时，复数就退化为实数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-number",
      "line_id": "complex-number-4",
      "filename": "complex-number-complex-number-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-number-complex-number-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.41,
      "size": 22608,
      "text": "当a等于0时，复数就是纯虚数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-plane",
      "line_id": "complex-plane-1",
      "filename": "complex-plane-complex-plane-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-plane-complex-plane-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "复数可以在平面上表示，这个平面叫做复平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-plane",
      "line_id": "complex-plane-2",
      "filename": "complex-plane-complex-plane-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-plane-complex-plane-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "横轴是实轴，表示实部；纵轴是虚轴，表示虚部。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-plane",
      "line_id": "complex-plane-3",
      "filename": "complex-plane-complex-plane-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-plane-complex-plane-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "每个复数对应平面上的一个点，反过来也成立。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "complex-plane",
      "line_id": "complex-plane-4",
      "filename": "complex-plane-complex-plane-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/complex-plane-complex-plane-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "拖动图中的点，观察它对应的复数如何变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "modulus-argument",
      "line_id": "modulus-argument-1",
      "filename": "modulus-argument-modulus-argument-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/modulus-argument-modulus-argument-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "复数还有另一种表示方法：用模和辐角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "modulus-argument",
      "line_id": "modulus-argument-2",
      "filename": "modulus-argument-modulus-argument-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/modulus-argument-modulus-argument-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 41040,
      "text": "模是复数到原点的距离，用r表示，等于a平方加b平方的平方根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "modulus-argument",
      "line_id": "modulus-argument-3",
      "filename": "modulus-argument-modulus-argument-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/modulus-argument-modulus-argument-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "辐角是复数与正实轴的夹角，用希腊字母θ表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "modulus-argument",
      "line_id": "modulus-argument-4",
      "filename": "modulus-argument-modulus-argument-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/modulus-argument-modulus-argument-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "这样，复数可以写成r乘以括号cos θ加i sin θ的形式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "euler-formula",
      "line_id": "euler-formula-1",
      "filename": "euler-formula-euler-formula-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/euler-formula-euler-formula-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.98,
      "size": 47664,
      "text": "数学中最美的公式之一是欧拉公式：e的iθ次方等于cos θ加i sin θ。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "euler-formula",
      "line_id": "euler-formula-2",
      "filename": "euler-formula-euler-formula-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/euler-formula-euler-formula-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "这个公式把指数函数和三角函数神奇地联系在一起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "euler-formula",
      "line_id": "euler-formula-3",
      "filename": "euler-formula-euler-formula-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/euler-formula-euler-formula-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "当θ等于π时，我们得到欧拉恒等式：e的iπ次方加1等于0。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "euler-formula",
      "line_id": "euler-formula-4",
      "filename": "euler-formula-euler-formula-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/euler-formula-euler-formula-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "这个等式包含了数学中最重要的五个常数：0、1、e、i和π。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "multiplication-1",
      "filename": "multiplication-multiplication-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/multiplication-multiplication-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.28,
      "size": 20448,
      "text": "复数乘法有一个美妙的几何意义。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "multiplication-2",
      "filename": "multiplication-multiplication-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/multiplication-multiplication-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "两个复数相乘，模相乘，辐角相加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "multiplication-3",
      "filename": "multiplication-multiplication-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/multiplication-multiplication-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "这意味着乘以一个复数，相当于旋转加缩放！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "multiplication-4",
      "filename": "multiplication-multiplication-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/multiplication-multiplication-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "特别地，乘以i相当于逆时针旋转90度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "multiplication-5",
      "filename": "multiplication-multiplication-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/multiplication-multiplication-5.mp3",
      "duration": 3.2,
      "size": 51264,
      "text": "这就解释了为什么i的平方等于负1：旋转两次90度就是180度，正好变成相反数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-1",
      "filename": "applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.22,
      "size": 19440,
      "text": "复数在很多领域都有重要应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-2",
      "filename": "applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "电气工程中，交流电路分析大量使用复数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-3",
      "filename": "applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "量子力学中，波函数就是复数值函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-4",
      "filename": "applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "信号处理中，傅里叶变换的结果是复数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-1",
      "filename": "summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.26,
      "size": 20160,
      "text": "让我们总结一下今天学到的内容。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-2",
      "filename": "summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "复数是实部加虚部的形式，可以在复平面上表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-3",
      "filename": "summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "复数的模是到原点的距离，辐角是与实轴的夹角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-4",
      "filename": "summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.37,
      "size": 21888,
      "text": "复数乘法的几何意义是旋转和缩放。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "complex",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-5",
      "filename": "summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/complex/xiaoxiao/summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "希望通过这个实验，你对复数有了更直观的理解！"
    }
  ],
